#. Translators: dialog title shown when trying to install the add-on on unsupported systems.
#: addon/installTasks.py:24
msgid "Enhanced Touch Gestures install warning"
msgstr "触摸屏手势增强安装警告"

#. No touch hardware whatsoever
#. Translators: dialog text shown when trying to install the add-on on unsupported systems.
#: addon/installTasks.py:29
msgid "This device does not support touch interaction. A touch capable device is required to use add-on features."
msgstr "此设备不支持触摸交互。需要具有触摸屏的设备才能使用插件功能。"

#. Portable NVDA running on a touch capable hardware
#. Translators: dialog text shown when trying to install the add-on on unsupported systems.
#: addon/installTasks.py:33
msgid "You are using a portable copy of NVDA and the device supports touch interaction. NVDA must be installed to use add-on features."
msgstr "您正在使用 NVDA 便携版，该设备支持触摸交互。必须安装 NVDA 才能使用插件功能。"

#. Translators: The gestures category for this add-on in input gestures dialog (2013.3 or later).
#. Add-on summary/title, usually the user visible name of the add-on
#. Translators: Summary/title for this add-on
#. to be shown on installation and add-on information found in add-on store
#: addon/globalPlugins/enhancedTouchGestures.py:38 buildVars.py:21
msgid "Enhanced Touch Gestures"
msgstr "触摸屏手势增强"

#. Translators: input help message for Enhanced touch Gestures command.
#: addon/globalPlugins/enhancedTouchGestures.py:226
msgid "Emulates pressing tab on the system keyboard"
msgstr "在系统键盘上模拟按下 Tab 键"

#. Translators: input help message for Enhanced touch Gestures command.
#: addon/globalPlugins/enhancedTouchGestures.py:234
msgid "Emulates pressing shift+tab on the system keyboard"
msgstr "在系统键盘上模拟按下 Shift+Tab 键"

#. Add-on description
#. Translators: Long description to be shown for this add-on on add-on information from add-on store
#: buildVars.py:24
msgid "A suite of additional touch commands, including navigation and help commands.\n"
"\tRequires a touch-enabled computer with Windows 8.1 or later with NVDA 2017.4 or later installed."
msgstr "一套附加的触摸手势，涵盖了导航和帮助命令。\n"
"需要安装了 NVDA 2017.4 或更高版本， Windows 8.1 或更高版本且带有触摸屏的电脑。"

#. Brief changelog for this version
#. Translators: what's new content for the add-on version to be shown in the add-on store
#: buildVars.py:30
msgid "* Renamed 'web mode' to 'browse mode' as this mode will cover additional situations including browse mode in Word 365."
msgstr "* 将“web 模式”重命名为“浏览模式”，因为此模式将涵盖其他情况，包括 Word 365中的浏览模式。"

